And I was like, no
wonder you won't believe,

00:32:11.620 --> 00:32:14.380
or you can't believe
that it's really me.

00:32:14.380 --> 00:32:15.730
Do you want me to send a selfie?

00:32:15.730 --> 00:32:16.940
He goes, yes please.

00:32:16.940 --> 00:32:18.210
And I did send a selfie.

00:32:18.210 --> 00:32:18.710
He loved it.

00:32:18.710 --> 00:32:21.390
FEMALE SPEAKER: You guys have
